_header: Hail Queen bliss of great honor
Note: May be a continuation of 1708 which precedes.
Subjects: Virgin Mary, hymns to; hymns, to Virgin Mary
_description: James Ryman, Salue regina — three stanzas rhyme royal

CULEe112.First Lines:
Hayle quene of blisse of gret honour moder of crist that king of
                    myght…
CULEe112.Last Lines:
…As he hath tolde to whome thou prayTo heuen blisse that we
                    comme may
